<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>yạ mnjy yạ mnjy</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sāyỉluⁿ nuʿ̊māka yal̊qay̱
 yā ạảbā ạlrãạ̊̉fah
 min̊ ladun̊ ʿar̊sẖika ḥālạaⁿ
 wāfira ạlrãḥ̊mah

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: yā munajĩy yā munajĩy
   ạản̊ta sul̊wānī
   tẖagẖ̊ruka ạl̊basãạmu yasẖ̊fī
   ḍaʿ̊fa ại̹ymānī

[V2]
 2- ại̹nãmā julũ murādī
 waj̊huka ạl̊waḍãạḥ̊
 fāsẖ̊fi jur̊ḥī biạl̊ḥasẖā
 yā mun̊yaẗa ạlạảr̊wāḥ̊

[V3]
 3- ạản̊ta yā kulã surūrī
 man̊baʿu ạlạảl̊ṭāf̊
 ạản̊ta lī kẖaẙru naṣībiⁿ
 yā sanī̃ ạlạảẘṣāf̊</lyrics>
<title>sạỷl nʿmạk ylqy̱</title>
<author>Doane, William Howard (1832-1915), Crosby, Fanny Jane (1820-1915)</author>
</song>